息14日?"},{"pid":"c368e2f0fb5d8df75da83437cb5c37c9b5b82bec","tid":1728320,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2337f5bc2e67c90b600fc2dd654e2fbb8c5764","tid":1728320,"uid":291322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ec3f9951cf425dc746c4446aa4c4d41de3deba7","tid":1728320,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d038228198c74450c37ac7d8e59e18362d283b","tid":1728320,"uid":291322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾點呀，邊有人睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:22:59.000Z","msg":"等陣啦！唔使心急。<br />\n我認同。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:24:28.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb97f249a1fa5274b16aa16ad71043442cd4817","tid":1728320,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e78bb081c76c3892382c26456386e7aa7729c52","tid":1728320,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:23:53.000Z","msg":"其實唔止疏導藍絲既情緒, 黃既都要, 我知大家唔洗休息, 但情緒要放鬆同文宣唔夠人<br />\n打14日, 休息7日?<br />\n打7日, 休息7日?<br />\n打7日, 休息14日?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:28:18.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲真係覺得解放軍出來係幫佢哋出咗啖氣，好撚得戚，合理化左老解違反駐軍法。"},{"pid":"c326188fd13ef0101d39bcf9d18d2b4cd53dc953","tid":1728320,"uid":340140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a24fe0ac91c1f41d97639b4208d054b7afa25619","tid":1728320,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb97f249a1fa5274b16aa16ad71043442cd4817","tid":1728320,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"